nodes.text: Star Wars: The Clone Wars – Original Soundtrack Seasons One Through Six

Star Wars: The Clone Wars – Original Soundtrack Seasons One Through Six is a soundtrack featuring music composed by Kevin Kiner for the first six seasons of Star Wars: The Clone Wars. Its issuance was planned since at least July 31, 2014. Walt Disney Records released the soundtrack on vinyl on November 9, 2014, and digitally on November 10.
